This git repository contains samples to help you use or create plugins for different business systems which allow you to share content with your Socialcast community.
To learn about the Socialcast product, please visit http://www.socialcast.com
To learn about integrating Socialcast with other business systems, please visit: http://developers.socialcast.com

=MediaWiki
Step by step installation guide is provided at: http://developers.socialcast.com/business-systems/mediawiki/

=WordPress
Step-by-step installation guide is provided at: http://developers.socialcast.com/business-systems/wordpress/